lead_paragraph: Lewis Hamilton outpaced his championship-leading Mercedes team mate Nico Rosberg in practice for the Malaysian Grand Prix on Friday, the Briton topping the timesheets with the fastest lap of the day.

headline.print_headline: Hamilton Finds Groove in Malaysia Practice
